room_title: Escape room "Baker Street Mystery" by Escape Room Alexandria in Alexandria (MN)
review: We tried our luck at Baker Street and even though we could have used 5 more minutes we all had a very good time. Looking forward to going back and trying another room.

room_title: Escape room "Baker Street Mystery" by Escape Room Alexandria in Alexandria (MN)
review: Our group had a blast playing the Baker Street Mystery room. Second escape room I've ever done and just as fun here in Alex as elsewhere. Check it out, you won't be disappointed!
